Network Lab Assignment || NIT Durgapur || 2022-2023

    ** Assignment ** : Write a simple TCP iterative server and client to evaluate arithmetic expressions.

    Assignment 2 : Write a simple TCP Concurrent server and client to evaluate arithmetic expressions.

    Assignment 3 : In this assignment, you are asked to write a client-server program using UDP sockets for viewing directory listings in a remote machine.

    Assignment 4 : Client program will send a string to a Server and Server will reply the client with a message telling whether the input string is palindrome or not.

    Assignment 5 : In this assignment, you will implement a simplified version of the file transfer protocol.

    Assignment 6 : You have to write a program where two players connect to a server in order to play the game of tic-tac-toe interactively.

    Assignment 7 : In this assignment, we will implement a simple chat server. Chat clients will connect to a central server S which will coordinate the chat.
